## The problem

Nowadays, whether you're in a creative industry, a technical industry,
business, or you would just like a corner of the internet to show off
your skills, the best way to centralize your portfolio is by having a
website. However, the truth is for a lot of people, where to start is
this big black box of tools, technology, dollar signs, and trying to
decide which one is the best fit for your business or portfolio.

